kalau begitu. / Kau juga.

415
00:36:04,998 --> 00:36:06,467
Aku harus menyalin ini.

416
00:36:25,818 --> 00:36:26,958
Hei, Ji Ah.

417
00:36:27,887 --> 00:36:30,657
Apa kau sudah selesaikan laporan
penjualan Elektronik Yumyung?

418
00:36:31,557 --> 00:36:33,057
